    "description": "<i>元之沙漏破碎，分裂成能够制造时间循环的两个灵体。<br><br>你将学习它们的行为与交互、以及这些交互如何干扰它们的时间循环。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/682d9f544b534a5b0e390d12c0c6b10d.poster.avif?t=1670492762\" width=420 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/682d9f544b534a5b0e390d12c0c6b10d.webm?t=1670492762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/682d9f544b534a5b0e390d12c0c6b10d.mp4?t=1670492762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>你能够理解循环时空的新规则吗?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >双生灵体——日与夜 </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/a430b1b6375d5252d11e72cb7bd82d2a.poster.avif?t=1670492762\" width=455 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/a430b1b6375d5252d11e72cb7bd82d2a.webm?t=1670492762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>您分别在白天和夜晚操控两个角色。它们看起来相似，但又各具特点。您需要借助其特点，发挥其最大优势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间循环和回放 </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/acb0a9914ad6404b73177fcff3b58a58.poster.avif?t=1670492762\" width=455 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/acb0a9914ad6404b73177fcff3b58a58.webm?t=1670492762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>您做出的移动都会被记录下来，并在控制另一角色时回放，相当于创建了小型时间循环。<br><br>注意，二者的回放并不相同：日之灵会倒带播放，而夜之灵会从头播放。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不必担心犯错 </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/7a4f80299eb7cc7db0f86aecc0638e52.poster.avif?t=1670492762\" width=455 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880490/extras/7a4f80299eb7cc7db0f86aecc0638e52.webm?t=1670492762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在这款游戏中你不会失败。无论何时，你都能够通过调整时间线及时修复错误！",
